2026-03-31T07:17:40.978155Z  INFO session_loop{thread_id=019d41cd-1eed-7b20-8604-a373d5f5a502}:submission_dispatch{otel.name="op.dispatch.user_input" submission.id="019d42bd-4289-7cb2-8998-062b3f0dfd7b" codex.op="user_input"}:turn{otel.name="session_task.turn" thread.id=019d41cd-1eed-7b20-8604-a373d5f5a502 turn.id=019d42bd-4289-7cb2-8998-062b3f0dfd7b model=gpt-5.4}: codex_core::stream_events_utils: ToolCall: exec_command {"cmd":"python - <<'PY'\nimport torch\nfrom pathlib import Path\np=sorted(Path('/workspace/video_bench/wan22_ti2v5b_vbench_16x4_seed42/latents').glob('*.pt'))[0]\nlat=torch.load(p,map_location='cpu')['latents']\nfor dtype in [torch.float32, torch.float16, torch.bfloat16, torch.int16, torch.int8]:\n    try:\n        if dtype.is_floating_point:\n            q=lat.to(dtype)\n        else:\n            scale = 127.0/max(lat.abs().max().item(),1e-8) if dtype==torch.int8 else 32767.0/max(lat.abs().max().item(),1e-8)\n            q=torch.round(lat*scale).to(dtype)\n        if q.dtype.is_floating_point:\n            r=q.to(torch.float32)\n        else:\n            inv=(max(lat.abs().max().item(),1e-8)/127.0 if dtype==torch.int8 else max(lat.abs().max().item(),1e-8)/32767.0)\n            r=q.to(torch.float32)*inv\n        mse=torch.mean((lat-r)**2).item()\n        peak=max(abs(lat.min().item()), abs(lat.max().item()))\n        psnr=99.0 if mse==0 else 20*torch.log10(torch.tensor(peak/(mse**0.5))).item()\n        print(dtype, 'mse', mse, 'psnr', psnr)\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(dtype, 'ERR', e)\nPY","yield_time_ms":1000,"max_output_tokens":2500} thread_id=019d41cd-1eed-7b20-8604-a373d5f5a502
